<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12142</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很快会有一个马车比赛。” 汤姆说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“各国的国王都会来参加，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看看谁的马车最快。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29160</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一定很好玩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猫咪舔了舔爪子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“感觉会很混乱。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只有一个国王赢，其他国王都输。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，国王们都不喜欢输。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47440</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“皇家魔法师们会在马车上施魔法。” 汤姆说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52539</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“最好的魔法才能赢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要准备一个好咒语。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆想了又想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64775</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了很多书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，汤姆来到了皇家养马场。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他举起魔杖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“马儿们，跑得快！马车，也快起来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！马车上出现了一对翅膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马的身上因为魔法闪着光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆笑了。“希望能成功！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，其他国王和魔法师们都到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109148</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个魔法师对汤姆挥手。是梅。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109148</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们是在魔法学校认识的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112358</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118744</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一个魔法师在大笑。是瓦尔特。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118744</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122880</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道哪个国王会输！” 瓦尔特说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122880</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126442</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“汤姆连简单的魔法都不会。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的马车一定很慢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆皱了皱眉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你等着，瓦尔特！” 他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的国王会赢的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！” 瓦尔特说，“等着瞧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>